    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've got to see this beauty\u2014it's honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one, and it's in absolutely flawless condition inside and out. No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. It drives like a total dream and has been kept in a climate-controlled garage. I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely fall in love with it. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
