    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a definitive example of the S54-powered legend. Meticulously maintained, the high-revving 3.2L inline-six features a fully serviced double-VANOS system and preventative rod bearing replacement. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis is rock-solid with documented subframe reinforcement and a factory-spec suspension setup that retains its original damping characteristics. Finished in flawless Carbon Black over Nappa leather, this vehicle displays zero mechanical parasitic loss and remains in showroom configuration.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. No accidents. Service records complete. Inspection welcome.",
      "price": 42500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality specimen that has been meticulously preserved since day one. This vehicle features a flawless exterior with a deep, glass-like finish, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. There are zero stone chips, dings, or swirl marks to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in 'time-capsule' condition; the premium leather seats are supple and free of any wear on the bolsters, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a comprehensive binder of records included. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage shows no signs of inclement weather exposure. It sits on a fresh set of high-performance tires and has been exclusively garage-kept and hand-washed. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are privileged to present this peerless example of automotive engineering, maintained to an exacting standard that mirrors its original showroom delivery. This vehicle exhibits a flawless exterior profile complemented by an interior cabin that remains in an impeccable, undisturbed state. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure peak performance, offering a driving experience that is both seamless and profound. For the collector or professional seeking a vehicle of rare pedigree and uncompromising quality, this acquisition represents an unrivaled opportunity.",
      "price": 43250.0,
