    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This specimen boasts a flawless subframe\u2014reinforced for longevity\u2014and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The suspension geometry remains factory-spec with fresh bushings, ensuring the legendary 50/50 weight distribution is felt through every corner. Every fluid service is documented, the rod bearings have been proactively addressed, and the compression across all six cylinders remains within 2% of factory tolerances. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior bolsters show zero sacrificial wear. This is a turn-key, mechanically synchronized masterpiece for the discerning purist.",
